nodes.documentation:
@title Pausable
@dev Base contract which allows children to implement an emergency stop mechanism.
linearizedBaseContracts.name: Pausable

parameters.documentation: @dev Modifier to make a function callable only when the contract is not paused.
parameters.name: whenNotPaused

parameters.documentation: @dev Modifier to make a function callable only when the contract is paused.
parameters.name: whenPaused

parameters.documentation: @dev called by the owner to pause, triggers stopped state

modifiers.documentation: @dev called by the owner to unpause, returns to normal state
